    plugins {
        register("androidApplicationBadging") {
            id                  = "convention.android.application.badging"
            implementationClass = "AndroidApplicationBadgingConventionPlugin"
        }
    }
}
```

Apply in the app module (alongside the application plugin):

```kotlin
